skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: is it e. f.
des:
Uses the isitef.com api to return the day and the count of the next upcoming Eurofurence.
All you have to do to get the remaining days until the next Eurofurence is say "Alexa, is it EF"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
